Content-Type: application/json

{
  "category": "supplement",
  "amount": 800.00,
  "notes": "Mineral lick"
}

###

### List expenses for a cow
GET {{baseUrl}}/cows/{{cowId}}/expenses
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ─────────────────────────────────────────
### MILK SALES
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Log a milk sale
POST {{baseUrl}}/milk-sales
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sale_date": "2026-04-04",
  "litres_sold": 120.5,
  "price_per_litre": 65.00,
  "buyer": "KCC",
  "notes": "Morning collection"
}

###

### List all milk sales
GET {{baseUrl}}/milk-sales
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### List milk sales for a specific month
GET {{baseUrl}}/milk-sales?month=2026-04
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

